OL,5, The price of some festive chocolate    
OL,6, boxes has risen by at least 50% in a   
OL,7, year, according to Which?              
OL,9,FWhile overall inflation for supermarket
OL,10,Ffood and drink eased in November to    
OL,11,F8.3%, the rise in the chocolate prices 
OL,12,Fwas significantly higher at 15.3%.     
OL,14,FThis has been blamed mainly on the     
OL,15,Fsoaring cost of cocoa, which has near  
OL,16,Fdoubled due to poor harvests in Africa.
OL,18,FWhich? has urged shoppers to compare   
OL,19,Fprices across retailers to get the best
OL,20,Fvalue.                                 
